  "body": "## Working Minecraft Versions\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>1.9, 1.10, 1.11, 1.12, 1.13, 1.14, 1.15, 1.16, 1.17, 1.18, 1.19 </strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Nowadays, you see that every <strong>Minecraft servers/SMPs</strong> has their own <strong>twist plugin</strong>, it could be <strong>original</strong> or <strong>not.</strong></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FUPzDkU.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" /></p>\n# Awakened SMP\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Awakened SMP</strong> is a <strong>special Minecraft server </strong>for&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Youtubers</span></strong>&nbsp;that has a <strong>plugin</strong> making you <strong>drop</strong> your <strong>head</strong> when someone <strong>kill</strong>s you, you could only <strong>respawn</strong> when someone else <strong>place down</strong> your <strong>head.</strong></span></p>\n# RespawnEggs\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>This plugin,</strong> which is <strong>similar</strong> to the <strong><span style=\"color: #800000;\">Awakened SMP</span>'s plugin.</strong> However, instead of <strong>dropping</strong> your <strong>head,</strong> you will be <strong>dropping</strong> your <strong><span style=\"color: #993300;\">egg</span></strong></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n# Donation\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #33cccc;\">Paypal:</span></strong> <strong>https://paypal.me/YM2IT</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ffcc00;\">Honeygain:</span>&nbsp;https://r.honeygain.me/DR3B6F8B0A</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Buymeacoffee: https://www.buymeacoffee.com/ym2it</strong></span></p>\n# Media\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">(No videos yet)</span></p>",
